Name: rnasieve
Version: 0.1.3
Summary: A library for the statistical deconvolution of RNA bulk samples with single-cell references.
Home-page: https://github.com/songlab-cal/rna-sieve
Author: Justin Hong
Author-email: justinhong@berkeley.edu
